<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-amy-l" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6222558); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6222558&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180052" alt="Dr_Amy L" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6222558)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-amy-l" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6222558); return false;">Dr_Amy L</a></span></p>
