<p><span id="u-credit-00483" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00483" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00483-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/blue-melody" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6733419); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6733419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180053" alt="blue_melody" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6733419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/blue-melody" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6733419); return false;">blue_melody</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1608362371 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">19 Dec 2020 07:19</span></p>
